metadata.name: Ice God #1
metadata.description:
Thousands of years in the making. Mythical gods of glacial origin.

Centuries of generative snowfall. Decades of compression. Millenia to form. Moments to dissolve. Leaving only myth of their existence and this NFT to live on forever.

An Ice God NFT is generated using photographs of icebergs and glacial ice from endangered glaciers in the Pacific Northwest and Alaska amassed by Janus Kober during his years as a sea kayak guide. Each piece of ice has melted long ago making this NFT all the more rare.
